 - Built-in input parameter files, such as masses,                7440 1451
   level density, discrete levels, fission barriers               7440 1451
   and gamma strength functions based on the RIPL                 7440 1451
   library [RIPL]                                                 7440 1451
 - Automatic retrieval of experimental data from the              7440 1451
   EXFOR library                                                  7440 1451
